## ⚙️ Planned Features
- [x] Rail-based movement with coordinate tracking
- [x] EV position sensing (placeholder for vision/marker)
- [x] Charging simulation logic
- [ ] Auto-detachment after full charge
- [ ] ROS service interface for control
- [ ] Multi-user queueing logic (planned)
- [ ] Manipulator integration (future)

